divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking back from the Store on Rt. 104 in Princeton, when I hear a low rumbling sound above my head. It was dark, and no cars around. I was near the Princeton Church of God. I looked straight up, where the sound was coming from and a black triangular craft flew slowly over my head. It was heading back towards the northeast, and flying probably around 25 to 30 miles per hour. It wasn't even maybe 60 feet above my head. I didn't catch any photos or anything, but needless to say, it weirded me out.
